
# 🤖 RAG-Based AI Study Assistant

A simple AI app that answers questions using **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)**.  
It retrieves relevant data from a dataset and generates accurate answers using an LLM.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

👉 https://bindu-19-code-endee-assignment.streamlit.app/

---

## 🚀 Overview

- Finds relevant information using embeddings  
- Generates answers based on retrieved context  
- Built with Streamlit  

---

## 🧠 System Design

User Query → Search → Context → LLM → Answer

---

## ⚙️ Use of Endee

- Used Endee as base repository  
- Built RAG pipeline on top of it  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python  
- Streamlit  
- Sentence Transformers  
- Scikit-learn  
- Groq API  

---

## 📂 Structure

```

bindu_endee_rag/
main.py
dataset.txt
requirements.txt

````

---

## 🔑 Setup

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run main.py
````

Add API key:

```
GROQ_API_KEY = "your_api_key"
```

